---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us"
  description="Learn more about our website, mission, content standards, and commitment to providing accurate and helpful information."
>
  <main class="container">
    <h1>About Us</h1>

    <p>
      Welcome to our website. We are an independent online publication focused on
      providing high-quality, well-researched, and easy-to-understand content
      related to technology, artificial intelligence, automation, and digital
      innovation.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      Our mission is to help readers understand complex topics in a simple and
      practical way. We aim to publish content that is informative, unbiased,
      and genuinely useful for learners, professionals, and enthusiasts.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Publish</h2>
    <p>
      The content on this website includes tutorials, explainers, how-to guides,
      and industry insights. Articles are created based on research, practical
      experience, and publicly available information.
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>Technology and software guides</li>
      <li>Artificial intelligence concepts and tools</li>
      <li>Automation workflows and productivity tips</li>
      <li>Educational and informational articles</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Content Standards</h2>
    <p>
      We strive to maintain high editorial standards. While some tools may be
      used to assist with drafting or research, all content is reviewed to ensure
      clarity, accuracy, and relevance before publication.
    </p>

    <h2>Advertising & Monetization</h2>
    <p>
      To support the maintenance of this website, we may display advertisements
      through services such as Google AdSense. Advertisements help keep the
      content free for readers.
    </p>
    <p>
      Any sponsored or affiliate content is disclosed clearly and does not
      influence our editorial integrity.
    </p>

    <h2>Transparency & Trust</h2>
    <p>
      We value transparency and user trust. Our goal is not to mislead users or
      promote unrealistic claims. Readers are encouraged to verify information
      and use their own judgment when applying any advice found on this website.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you have questions, feedback, or suggestions, please feel free to reach
      out through our contact page.
    </p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
